<collectingCountry box="[151,270,653,678]" name="Greenland" pageId="14" pageNumber="307">Greenland</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[282,364,653,678]" name="Iceland" pageId="14" pageNumber="307">Iceland</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[421,485,653,678]" name="Spain" pageId="14" pageNumber="307">Spain</collectingCountry>
south to the Gulf of 
<collectingCountry box="[722,806,653,678]" name="Guinea-Bissau" pageId="14" pageNumber="307">Guinea</collectingCountry>
, being more common south of 
<number box="[1158,1189,654,678]" pageId="14" pageNumber="307" value="40.0">40</number>
°N. Vulnerability: DD (
<collectionCode box="[159,233,690,714]" pageId="14" pageNumber="307">IUCN</collectionCode>
), MV (FishBase).
</paragraph>
